# - smoke-claimondo-de/iter*-raw-log.json → Smoke-Roh-Output
# - smoke-claimondo-de/prod-iter-*/ → Screenshots aus alten Smoke-Iters
.claude/worktrees/
.claude/skill/
agents-runner/
